Package com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao

Interface LocationDAO

All Known Implementing Classes:
LocationDAOImpl
public interface LocationDAO
Interface for Data Access Object (DAO) related to the Location entity. This interface provides a contract for CRUD operations on the Location entity, as well as querying by specific criteria.
